title: Comment on Drake goes to the Cheesecake Factory in the video for “Child’s Play” — watch by Gunwitch
text:
Reddit 
“”Why you gotta fight with me at Cheesecake/ You know I love to go there,” raps Drake on the Views track “Child’s Play”. That real-life nightmare in played out in the song’s accompanying video, as Drizzy’s girl (played by Tyra Banks) lets loose over slices of Chocolate Mousse. As the 12-minute clip progresses, Drake makes his way to a Toronto strip club. Watch it all below via Apple Music. Artists
